{"tw": {"3536260": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "染色的純白", "steam_appid": 3536260, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3536260/extras/edbbe078b0190f21eb03f171a8e240c4.avif?t=1758942886\" width=616 height=147 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在像北奧拉王國這樣的階級社會中，身為平民的隼人必須崛起，以保護自己的村莊。與青梅竹馬莉亞一同，他踏上了成為聖騎士的修煉之路——然而，其他男人的慾望卻威脅著她的純潔。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你能否實現自己的目標，守護莉亞？還是會讓她被其他男人奪走？在這款NTR RPG中，你的每個決定都將左右他們最終的命運。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3536260/extras/fe8e2d80dab85f5998605ab40463ff05.avif?t=1758942886\" width=616 height=147 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扮演隼人，踏上成為聖騎士的危險旅程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >透過簡單易上手的回合制RPG戰鬥系統擊敗敵人。無需反覆練級或管理物品欄，即可快速推進故事發展。透過在王都中搜集線索，找到與莉亞共度幸福結局的方法，守護她免遭腐化——否則，你可能會親眼目睹她投入別的男人懷抱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >集中你的智慧，信賴你的直覺，做出最正確的選擇來保護她……否則，你將會失去她。窺探她的記憶與內心，揭開她隱藏的一面。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3536260/extras/e60426d03efa8ecf883a1d2d9f97b894.avif?t=1758942886\" width=616 height=147 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3536260/extras/d842b15962608ef764a8b0677575ad5f.avif?t=1758942886\" width=616 height=469 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3536260/extras/f253d01615361584c91b89862b55177b.avif?t=1758942886\" width=616 height=469 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3536260/extras/05c2d12f41e56f26374c735faefc57cd.avif?t=1758942886\" width=616 height=469 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3536260/extras/fd9e057dd9d583d7a12c0b02db5a8927.avif?t=1758942886\" width=616 height=469 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3536260/extras/8f400315bedb21855ab992bfb090dc02.avif?t=1758942886\" width=616 height=469 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3536260/extras/2dab65e26799ae2f997b4f70eb3d7513.avif?t=1758942886\" width=616 height=469 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3536260/extras/5d5aae291e1143851440672061705745.avif?t=1758942886\" width=616 height=469 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3536260/extras/fc2029253b1f9dffa69963e848683d5a.avif?t=1758942886\" width=616 height=147 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>抉擇至關重要</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >旅途中，你的選擇將影響故事的發展方向。多種結局等待著你，確保解鎖所有可能的結局吧！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>輕鬆戰鬥</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用隼人和莉亞的非凡天賦與默契配合，輕鬆應對戰鬥，暢快推進冒險！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>莉亞的不同形態</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >見證莉亞在旅途中的變化！你的青梅竹馬展現出的各種不同形態，等待你去發掘！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>回憶室</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >重溫隼人和莉亞的回憶，回顧他們的過去與經歷。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>尋找隱藏線索</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在王都中尋找隱藏的關鍵線索，幫助你達成理想中的幸福結局！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>二周目模式</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >開啟新遊戲+，可選擇從故事開端或分支劇情開始你的新旅程！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3536260/extras/edbbe078b0190f21eb03f171a8e240c4.avif?t=1758942886\" width=616 height=147 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在像北奧拉王國這樣的階級社會中，身為平民的隼人必須崛起，以保護自己的村莊。與青梅竹馬莉亞一同，他踏上了成為聖騎士的修煉之路——然而，其他男人的慾望卻威脅著她的純潔。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你能否實現自己的目標，守護莉亞？還是會讓她被其他男人奪走？在這款NTR RPG中，你的每個決定都將左右他們最終的命運。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3536260/extras/fe8e2d80dab85f5998605ab40463ff05.avif?t=1758942886\" width=616 height=147 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扮演隼人，踏上成為聖騎士的危險旅程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >透過簡單易上手的回合制RPG戰鬥系統擊敗敵人。無需反覆練級或管理物品欄，即可快速推進故事發展。透過在王都中搜集線索，找到與莉亞共度幸福結局的方法，守護她免遭腐化——否則，你可能會親眼目睹她投入別的男人懷抱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >集中你的智慧，信賴你的直覺，做出最正確的選擇來保護她……否則，你將會失去她。窺探她的記憶與內心，揭開她隱藏的一面。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3536260/extras/e60426d03efa8ecf883a1d2d9f97b894.avif?t=1758942886\" width=616 height=147 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3536260/extras/d842b15962608ef764a8b0677575ad5f.avif?t=1758942886\" width=616 height=469 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3536260/extras/f253d01615361584c91b89862b55177b.avif?t=1758942886\" width=616 height=469 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3536260/extras/05c2d12f41e56f26374c735faefc57cd.avif?t=1758942886\" width=616 height=469 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3536260/extras/fd9e057dd9d583d7a12c0b02db5a8927.avif?t=1758942886\" width=616 height=469 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3536260/extras/8f400315bedb21855ab992bfb090dc02.avif?t=1758942886\" width=616 height=469 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3536260/extras/2dab65e26799ae2f997b4f70eb3d7513.avif?t=1758942886\" width=616 height=469 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3536260/extras/5d5aae291e1143851440672061705745.avif?t=1758942886\" width=616 height=469 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3536260/extras/fc2029253b1f9dffa69963e848683d5a.avif?t=1758942886\" width=616 height=147 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>抉擇至關重要</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >旅途中，你的選擇將影響故事的發展方向。多種結局等待著你，確保解鎖所有可能的結局吧！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>輕鬆戰鬥</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用隼人和莉亞的非凡天賦與默契配合，輕鬆應對戰鬥，暢快推進冒險！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>莉亞的不同形態</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >見證莉亞在旅途中的變化！你的青梅竹馬展現出的各種不同形態，等待你去發掘！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>回憶室</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >重溫隼人和莉亞的回憶，回顧他們的過去與經歷。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>尋找隱藏線索</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在王都中尋找隱藏的關鍵線索，幫助你達成理想中的幸福結局！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>二周目模式</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >開啟新遊戲+，可選擇從故事開端或分支劇情開始你的新旅程！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>", "short_description": "一款劇情刺激、擁有多重結局的輕度NTR RPG。扮演隼人，與美麗的莉亞一同追尋聖騎士之路。窺探她的內心，守護她不被他人染指。在充滿誘惑的世界裡，你能守護她的純潔嗎？", "supported_languages": "英文, 日文, 簡體中文, 繁體中文", "header_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3536260/95af0073b254337119c747cf90a4950d3cba7cc5/header_tchinese.jpg?t=1758942886", "capsule_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3536260/2744a67cc2c9f739143d37af5d5472df48ab2a52/capsule_231x87_tchinese.jpg?t=1758942886", "capsule_imagev5": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3536260/2744a67cc2c9f739143d37af5d5472df48ab2a52/capsule_184x69_tchinese.jpg?t=1758942886", "website": null, "pc_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>最低配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>作業系統 *:</strong> Windows® 7/8/8.1/10<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> Intel Core2 Duo or better<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 4 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> DirectX 9/OpenGL 4.1 capable GPU<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 1 GB 可用空間</li></ul>"}, "mac_requirements": [], "linux_requirements": [], "legal_notice": "2025 Saikey Studios", "developers": ["Sinabi Ninja Village"], "publishers": ["Saikey Studios"], "price_overview": {"currency": "TWD", "initial": 23800, "final": 23800, "discount_percent": 0, "initial_formatted": "", "final_formatted": "NT$ 238"}, "categories": [{"id": 2, "description": "單人"}, {"id": 22, "description": "Steam 成就"}, {"id": 18, "description": "部分控制器支援"}, {"id": 23, "description": "Steam 雲端"}, {"id": 62, "description": "親友同享"}], "genres": [{"id": "25", "description": "冒險"}, {"id": "3", "description": "角色扮演"}], "release_date": {"coming_soon": false, "date": "2025 年 9 月 26 日"}}}}, "us": {"3536260": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Dyed in White", "steam_appid": 3536260, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3536260/extras/0a6e9786c60ebbcb5fcb3d465084904d.avif?t=1758942886\" width=616 height=147 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a class-based society like the North Aura Kingdom, a lowborn Hayato must rise to protect his village. Alongside his childhood friend Leia, he trains to become a Holy Knight—but other men’s desires threaten her purity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you be able to achieve your goal and protect Leia? Or will you let someone else win her over? It is up to you to decide what fate awaits them at the end of their intense story in this NTR RPG.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3536260/extras/c1303b615844c9a4d235d7e04f2cc274.avif?t=1758942886\" width=616 height=147 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as Hayato on his dangerous journey to become a Holy Knight. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Blast through enemies with the simple and easy turn based RPG combat system. Progress through the story quickly without the need to level up or thinking about managing your inventory. Gather clues throughout the capital to reach your desired happy ending with Leia, and protect her from being corrupted throughout your journey, or risk seeing her taken into another man's arms.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gather your wits, trust your intuition, and choose the best choice to protect her... or you might lose her forever. Discover her hidden side by peeking through her memories and heart.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3536260/extras/e8293e227b7a7858855bbdc4834e99cc.avif?t=1758942886\" width=616 height=147 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3536260/extras/0c01d9b24fa734ccaf30e4b4c5ecfaea.avif?t=1758942886\" width=616 height=469 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3536260/extras/ac6efb31b0f1ee231cb6d4bb6d9dd47d.avif?t=1758942886\" width=616 height=469 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3536260/extras/7ca97c80104dc1c688c19d3615fa911e.avif?t=1758942886\" width=616 height=469 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3536260/extras/694235c07b8ccb9338e2827a0ca3f193.avif?t=1758942886\" width=616 height=469 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3536260/extras/6dc1a2927d85beb3f82c1c9fa985e7d3.avif?t=1758942886\" width=616 height=469 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3536260/extras/cc4deff9f944c48aa64a60d5d9888728.avif?t=1758942886\" width=616 height=469 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3536260/extras/978995ae93214dddc1e7d6a5bad9be07.avif?t=1758942886\" width=616 height=469 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3536260/extras/6a5ede9f92478446617494764f7d86c9.avif?t=1758942886\" width=616 height=147 /></span><strong>Choice Matters</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >During your journey, you will have to make choices that will have an impact on the path of the story. Several endings are waiting for you at the end of your journey, make sure to get them all!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Laidback Combat</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Breeze through the combat easily by using Hayato and Leia's extraordinary talents and teamwork!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Different Form of Leia's Appearances</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Watch Leia's transformation throughout the journey! Several different appearances of your childhood friend are waiting for you to discover! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Reminiscence Room</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Relive both of Hayato and Leia's memories and past experiences in the reminiscence room.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Search for Hidden Clues</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Search for important clues hidden inside the capital to aid you on your mission as you reach for your desired happy ending!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>New Game Plus</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Start a new game plus with the option of choosing whether to start from the beginning of the story or from a branching story route.</p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3536260/extras/0a6e9786c60ebbcb5fcb3d465084904d.avif?t=1758942886\" width=616 height=147 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a class-based society like the North Aura Kingdom, a lowborn Hayato must rise to protect his village. Alongside his childhood friend Leia, he trains to become a Holy Knight—but other men’s desires threaten her purity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you be able to achieve your goal and protect Leia? Or will you let someone else win her over? It is up to you to decide what fate awaits them at the end of their intense story in this NTR RPG.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3536260/extras/c1303b615844c9a4d235d7e04f2cc274.avif?t=1758942886\" width=616 height=147 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as Hayato on his dangerous journey to become a Holy Knight. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Blast through enemies with the simple and easy turn based RPG combat system. Progress through the story quickly without the need to level up or thinking about managing your inventory. Gather clues throughout the capital to reach your desired happy ending with Leia, and protect her from being corrupted throughout your journey, or risk seeing her taken into another man's arms.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gather your wits, trust your intuition, and choose the best choice to protect her... or you might lose her forever. Discover her hidden side by peeking through her memories and heart.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3536260/extras/e8293e227b7a7858855bbdc4834e99cc.avif?t=1758942886\" width=616 height=147 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3536260/extras/0c01d9b24fa734ccaf30e4b4c5ecfaea.avif?t=1758942886\" width=616 height=469 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3536260/extras/ac6efb31b0f1ee231cb6d4bb6d9dd47d.avif?t=1758942886\" width=616 height=469 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3536260/extras/7ca97c80104dc1c688c19d3615fa911e.avif?t=1758942886\" width=616 height=469 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3536260/extras/694235c07b8ccb9338e2827a0ca3f193.avif?t=1758942886\" width=616 height=469 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3536260/extras/6dc1a2927d85beb3f82c1c9fa985e7d3.avif?t=1758942886\" width=616 height=469 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3536260/extras/cc4deff9f944c48aa64a60d5d9888728.avif?t=1758942886\" width=616 height=469 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3536260/extras/978995ae93214dddc1e7d6a5bad9be07.avif?t=1758942886\" width=616 height=469 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3536260/extras/6a5ede9f92478446617494764f7d86c9.avif?t=1758942886\" width=616 height=147 /></span><strong>Choice Matters</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >During your journey, you will have to make choices that will have an impact on the path of the story. Several endings are waiting for you at the end of your journey, make sure to get them all!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Laidback Combat</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Breeze through the combat easily by using Hayato and Leia's extraordinary talents and teamwork!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Different Form of Leia's Appearances</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Watch Leia's transformation throughout the journey! Several different appearances of your childhood friend are waiting for you to discover! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Reminiscence Room</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Relive both of Hayato and Leia's memories and past experiences in the reminiscence room.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Search for Hidden Clues</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Search for important clues hidden inside the capital to aid you on your mission as you reach for your desired happy ending!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>New Game Plus</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Start a new game plus with the option of choosing whether to start from the beginning of the story or from a branching story route.</p>", "short_description": "A laid-back NTR RPG with a thrilling story and multiple endings. As Hayato, pursue becoming a Holy Knight alongside beautiful Leia. Delve into her deepest thoughts and shield her from other men. Can you protect her purity in a world full of temptation?", "supported_languages": "English, Japanese, Simplified Chinese, Traditional Chinese", "header_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3536260/65fbcb3778bd1ae2f8113923b08ce86e8d49bbfc/header.jpg?t=1758942886", "capsule_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3536260/5cdbb05f06c8ab30537d16a5e665e8691c22c05d/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1758942886", "capsule_imagev5": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3536260/5cdbb05f06c8ab30537d16a5e665e8691c22c05d/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1758942886", "website": null, "pc_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS *:</strong> Windows® 7/8/8.1/10<br></li><li><strong>Processor:</strong> Intel Core2 Duo or better<br></li><li><strong>Memory:</strong> 4 GB RAM<br></li><li><strong>Graphics:</strong> DirectX 9/OpenGL 4.1 capable GPU<br></li><li><strong>Storage:</strong> 1 GB available space</li></ul>"}, "mac_requirements": [], "linux_requirements": [], "legal_notice": "2025 Saikey Studios", "developers": ["Sinabi Ninja Village"], "publishers": ["Saikey Studios"], "price_overview"